short_description:
UnrealGoldFix is a set of .u packages for Unreal:

* UGoldFix - resolves several issues related to single-player and multiplayer modes; 
* AI_Mutator - makes monsters more aggressive, dodgy, and accurate at shooting;
* CustomFilter - applies custom filters to Actors;
* MoverProtection - prevents Movers from being blocked;
* PermanentFragments - prevents Carcasses, Fragments, BigRocks, and tossed Weapons from disappearing.

Supported game versions: 224, 225f, 226a/final, 226b, 227i
